<name key="馮京" type="givenName">京</name>再執政<pc>，</pc>初與<persName>王安石</persName>不合<pc>，</pc>後為呂惠卿所傾<pc>，</pc>其中立不倚之操<pc>，</pc>為先帝稱挹<pc>。</pc>且昭陵學士<pc>，</pc>獨<name key="馮京" type="givenName">京</name>
<measure quantity="1" unit="people">
